{
  "stem": "12447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember we used to come to various functions, like parties and birthdays of my cousins.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CRYING] I remember, on my father's side-- my father comes from a different town, not from Warsaw, which is about 100 kilometers east of Warsaw, that took about two or three hours by train.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I traveled with my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my grandmother lived there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The time was called Siedlce.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's S-I-E-D-L-E-- I have to look.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's C-E, I believe, Siedlce, if I can memorize it correctly to spelling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I traveled there about once a year with my father to visit his mother and his sister, which lived with my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- my, my, my aunt, my father's sister, was a what they used to call her in quiet, an old maid.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was probably a, a, a lady in her 30s, as I can remember her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was very nice-- [CRYING] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother-- my grandmother, of course, she was-- she owned a, a flour mill.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the peasants would come to mill their grains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would bring all the goodies, like fresh rolls and fresh bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I enjoyed it very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember those times that I traveled there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I liked it very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't wait for the day that my father would say, well, let's go see my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[CRYING] So that's part of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Siedlce, at that point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then getting back, of course, to Warsaw, to my home, I remember my first day of school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember [CRYING] they put me in school quite, quite premature, they said.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
